<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1486018-this-is-a-magnificent-human-document-that">This is a magnificent human document that fulfills the promise given in its subtitle. The sweep of its subject matter and its engagement with individual lives give it true epic proportions. Isn&#39;t it is surely one of the great books written in our time?</a>
</div>
